+	 * upon fault during which the accessed bit is set, add it to the
+	 * youngest generation.
+	 *
+	 * If a page can't be evicted immediately, i.e., an anon page not in
+	 * swap cache or a dirty page pending writeback, add it to the second
+	 * oldest generation.
